data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4 bed, 3 bath home in the Bridges. With its beautiful design and abundance of natural light, this property offers a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the kitchen, dining area, and living room. The kitchen features elegant granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and oversized walk-in pantry. Cozy up by the fireplace in the living room or step outside to the covered patio overlooking the spacious backyard and manicured golf course. The primary suite includes a generous walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom with dual sinks. Game-room or second living down stairs with loads of natural light.  Barrel vaulted brick foyer welcomes you in and opens to spacious home office.  Guest suite down with full bath.  Two bedrooms with jack and jill up along with flex space.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this house your own sweet home!
